<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何重大新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 09:15:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>6月中国汽车销量连续第三个月下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-slide-june-falling-third-month-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国6月份汽车销量同比下降6.9%，连续第三个月下滑，原因是政府的激励措施未能在经济复苏缓慢的情况下刺激消费者需求。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:11:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-car-sales-slide-june-falling-third-month-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利总理在与中国国家主席习近平会谈后前往华盛顿</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/hungarys-pm-travels-washington-after-talks-with-chinas-xi-2024-07-08/</link><description>匈牙利总理欧尔班维克托周一表示，他在北京讨论了中国对乌克兰的和平计划后将前往华盛顿。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 08:00:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/hungarys-pm-travels-washington-after-talks-with-chinas-xi-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>当地媒体称，中国可能调查储能电站的火灾风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-may-investigate-energy-storage-plants-fire-risks-local-media-says-2024-07-08/</link><description>据《21世纪经济报道》周一报道，中国当局正在考虑下令对储能工厂进行大规模火灾风险调查，这表明中国蓬勃发展的电池储能行业标准更加严格。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 07:21:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/china-may-investigate-energy-storage-plants-fire-risks-local-media-says-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>日本表示热衷于深化与菲律宾、美国和澳大利亚的安全关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-says-keen-deepen-security-ties-with-philippines-us-australia-2024-07-08/</link><description>日本防卫大臣周一表示，日本热衷于在三边和四边安排下深化与菲律宾、美国和澳大利亚的安全关系。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 05:43:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-says-keen-deepen-security-ties-with-philippines-us-australia-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>早盘：法军左翼包抄右翼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-08/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 04:35:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>据国际文传电讯社报道，两艘俄罗斯军舰被派往亚太海域执行训练任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/two-russian-warships-sent-training-mission-asia-pacific-waters-interfax-reports-2024-07-08/</link><description>国际文传电讯社周一援引俄罗斯海军太平洋舰队新闻部门的消息称，俄罗斯海军太平洋舰队的两艘护卫舰离开俄罗斯远东符拉迪沃斯托克港，前往亚太地区执行训练任务。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:36:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/two-russian-warships-sent-training-mission-asia-pacific-waters-interfax-reports-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>黄金因获利了结而从五月高点回落</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-lingers-near-one-month-high-fed-rate-cut-bets-2024-07-08/</link><description>周一金价下跌，因美国九月降息押注增加，金价在前一交易日触及一个多月高点后，投资者获利了结。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 03:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-lingers-near-one-month-high-fed-rate-cut-bets-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行调整流动性操作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-central-bank-tweaks-liquidity-operations-amid-strong-bond-demand-2024-07-08/</link><description>中国央行周一表示，将启动临时债券回购协议或逆回购协议，以提高公开市场操作效率，保持银行体系流动性充裕。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 02:59:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-central-bank-tweaks-liquidity-operations-amid-strong-bond-demand-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾和日本在南海紧张局势中签署防务协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-japan-sign-landmark-defence-deal-2024-07-08/</link><description>菲律宾和日本周一签署了互惠准入协议（RAA），加强了防务关系，称在与中国的紧张局势加剧之际，两国正在寻求该地区的稳定。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 02:51:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-japan-sign-landmark-defence-deal-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>欧元因法国僵局而下滑；非农就业数据出乎意料之后美元走软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-eases-french-poll-gridlock-dollar-sluggish-after-us-payrolls-2024-07-08/</link><description>法国大选预测显示，由于左翼联盟出乎意料地强劲，法国大选将出现悬浮议会，欧元周一下跌，这给该国的财政前景带来了新的不确定性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 01:14:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/euro-eases-french-poll-gridlock-dollar-sluggish-after-us-payrolls-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市小幅走高，欧元受法国政治僵局困扰</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-08/</link><description>亚洲股市周一小幅走高，因投资者对美国 9 月降息信心增强，而法国大选表明议会将出现悬浮议会，欧元则面临政治不确定性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-08/</guid></item><item><title>匈牙利总统欧尔班出人意料地访华，支持习近平的和平计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hungary-pm-orban-arrives-beijing-talks-with-chinese-president-xi-2024-07-07/</link><description>匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克多周一会见了中国国家主席习近平，讨论了可能达成的乌克兰和平协议。在与俄罗斯总统普京的会谈激怒了一些欧盟领导人几天后，他出人意料地访问了北京。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hungary-pm-orban-arrives-beijing-talks-with-chinese-president-xi-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国影响力的增强，美国和澳大利亚致力于改善太平洋银行业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-commits-bolstering-financial-connectivity-pacific-2024-07-07/</link><description>美国和澳大利亚官员周一表示，他们致力于改善太平洋地区的金融互联互通，在中国兴趣日益浓厚的情况下，该地区的贷款机构和政策制定者开会讨论加强银行服务的问题。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 23:22:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/us-commits-bolstering-financial-connectivity-pacific-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜金与正指责韩国领导人利用紧张局势来分散政治注意力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-yo-jong-calls-south-korean-drills-provocation-kcna-says-2024-07-07/</link><description>官方媒体周一称，朝鲜领导人金正恩的妹妹金与正指责韩国总统尹淑烈在朝鲜半岛制造紧张局势，以转移人们对国内问题的注意力。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:56:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-koreas-kim-yo-jong-calls-south-korean-drills-provocation-kcna-says-2024-07-07/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：乐观情绪高涨，软着陆步入正轨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-07/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2024 21:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-07-07/</guid></item></channel></rss>